OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773662584
OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FThe war, which began with joint
OL,7,FIsraeli-US strikes on Iran on February
OL,8,F28, has spread across the Middle East.
OL,9,FIsraeli strikes have killed more than
OL,10,F850 people in Lebanon and displaced at
OL,11,Fleast 850,000 people.
OL,13,FIsrael has launched new attacks on
OL,14,FBeirut and Tehran, while Dubai's
OL,15,Fairport suspended flights after an
OL,16,FIranian drone hit a nearby fuel tank
OL,17,Fand sparked a fire. Iran also launched
OL,18,Fmissiles towards Israel on Monday.
OL,20,FSome flights resume at Dubai airport
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
