OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FA dronerelated incident sparked a
OL,7,Ffire near Dubai International Airport
OL,8,Fon Monday, forcing a temporary
OL,9,Fsuspension of flights, the city's
OL,10,Fmedia office said on X. United Arab
OL,11,FEmirates officials say Dubai
OL,12,FInternational Airport has gradually
OL,13,Fresumed some flights after a drone
OL,14,Fstrike.
OL,16,FThe blaze was successfully contained
OL,17,Fand no injuries were reported, but
OL,18,Flocal aviation authorities halted
OL,19,Foperations as a precaution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
