PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773662584
OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FEmirates was among the major airlines
OL,7,Fto confirm its flights had been
OL,8,Fgrounded, telling passengers on X:
OL,9,F"Please do not go to the airport.
OL,11,F"Emirates will share updates when
OL,12,Favailable. We would like to thank our
OL,13,Fcustomers for their understanding and
OL,14,Fpatience."
OL,16,FEmirates later said it would operate
OL,17,Fon a "limited schedule" from 10am
OL,18,Flocal time, but "some flights from
OL,19,Ftoday's schedule have been cancelled".
OL,21,FSaudi Arabia reports drone attacks
