OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FSaudi Arabia says it intercepted three
OL,7,Fdrones on Monday morning over the
OL,8,Fcapital Riyadh and the nation's oil-
OL,9,Frich western region.
OL,11,FThe Saudi Defense Ministry says no
OL,12,Fcasualties or damage were reported.
OL,14,FThe ministry reports that more than 60
OL,15,Fdrones attacked the Gulf country
OL,16,Fwithin a few hours.
OL,18,FBrent crude trades near $105
OL,20,FBrent crude oil is trading near the
OL,21,F$105 a barrel level on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
