OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FA barrel of Brent, the international
OL,7,Fstandard, was up 1.6% at $104.73,
OL,8,Fdipping slightly after opening above
OL,9,F$106 per barrel. It's up more than 40%
OL,10,Fsince the war began.
OL,12,FShare prices in Asia were mixed and US
OL,13,Ffutures advanced.
