OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FThe United Arab Emirates' Defense
OL,7,FMinistry said forces were intercepting
OL,8,FIranian missiles and drones Monday
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FStarmer and Trump discuss 'importance'
OL,12,Fof reopening Strait of Hormuz
OL,14,FStarmer will pledge to help households
OL,15,Fwith the cost of living amid the
OL,16,Fenergy price spike caused by the war
OL,17,Fin the Middle East, after he appeared
OL,18,Fto resist Donald Trump's calls to send
OL,19,Fwarships to the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
