PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773662584
OL,3,CTrump steps up pressure on allies over
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as strikes continue
OL,6,FTehran's stranglehold on oil tankers
OL,7,Fpassing through the narrow sea passage
OL,8,Fhas driven energy prices up across the
OL,9,Fworld.
OL,11,FA Downing Street spokeswoman said the
OL,12,Fpair "discussed the ongoing situation
OL,13,Fin the Middle East and the importance
OL,14,Fof reopening the Strait of Hormuz to
OL,15,Fend the disruption to global shipping,
OL,16,Fwhich is driving up costs worldwide".
OL,18,F"The prime minister also expressed his
OL,19,Fcondolences for the American service
OL,20,Fpersonnel who have lost their lives
OL,21,Fduring the conflict," she added.
